query: How did the top teams achieve sub-69 scores in Santa 2025 Kaggle Christmas tree packing competition? What techniques or private data sources did they use?

results.title: ANSWER
results.text: Top teams in the Santa 2025 Kaggle competition achieved sub-69 scores primarily through advanced optimization techniques and ensemble models, but specific details about the techniques or private data sources they used are not publicly disclosed in the available sources ([Kaggle Santa 2025](https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/santa-2025)).
